<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Forgot Password - ZipZap</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
      /* Base Styles */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222;
      }

      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      /* Layout */
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #fff;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      /* Button */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 12px 24px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Reset Password - ZipZap</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>
          We received a request to reset your password for your ZipZap account.
        </p>
        <p>Please use the following code to reset your password:</p>
        <h1><%= otp %></h1>
        <p>This OTP is valid for the next 5 minutes.</p>
        <p>
          If you didnâ€™t request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your
          account will remain secure.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>For any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The ZipZap Team</p>
        <p><a href="https://zipzap.com" class="button">Visit ZipZap</a></p>
        <p>
          <a href="mailto:support@zipzap.com" class="button">Contact Support</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
